{"tid":2002242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女文員咬傷休班黨衛軍 判囚兩周","createTime":"2020-05-05T05:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T05:58:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c21e60fbb3a5eb4cd201835779ad35f6a01c4c68","tid":2002242,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"女文員咬傷休班警 判囚兩周<br />\n2020-05-05 HKT 13:25<br />\n<br />\n一名女文員去年反修例運動期間涉嫌咬傷一名休班警員，判囚14天。<br />\n<br />\n27歲被告早前承認一項襲警罪，今日在東區裁判法院判刑。辯方求情時引述被告的心理報告指，被告對犯事感到後悔，重犯機會低，年少時從內地來港，因學業問題患上抑鬱，至今仍須定期覆診，但病情穩定。辯方又說，被告沒有案底，今次還押令她受到牢獄之苦，亦被公司停職，未知何時能復職。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官香淑嫻認為，雖然被告的報告正面，重犯機會低，但緩刑並不合適，因此判她監禁。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，去年11月民間「曙光行動」期間，被告謝穎希在港鐵灣仔站「衝閘」，一名休班警員上前截查並表露身份，被告企圖逃走，兩人糾纏雙雙倒地，被告隔著口罩咬休班警員的右臂近一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524311-20200505.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524311-20200505.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=496116b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524311-20200505.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=35a92db6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524311-20200505.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e888fa504c09bf1b6093342ef36d5b6b965ad094","tid":2002242,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"印證天琦講既說話，唔係睇邊度出生，係睇你認唔認同呢套價值觀"},{"pid":"a26d2f35e5350c74d6831e0ab923c38d1cee8def","tid":2002242,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:51:02.000Z","msg":"好似已經還柙夠"},{"pid":"9007e2d72035ce7c3dab6a76095d95a3839fd6ad","tid":2002242,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"心地善良<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caaaefc352a3036c60fc68ed28e122997